---
---
<section class="quote-section" aria-labelledby="quote-heading">
  <h2 id="quote-heading" class="visually-hidden">Featured quote</h2>
  <span class="quote-marks" aria-hidden="true">"</span>
  <p class="quote-eyebrow">§ 04 — A line I keep coming back to</p>
  <blockquote class="quote-text">
    <span class="quote-line"><span class="quote-line-inner">I think when you give your fullest in</span></span>
    <span class="quote-line"><span class="quote-line-inner">something you genuinely care about,</span></span>
    <span class="quote-line"><span class="quote-line-inner">the result reaches you on its own.</span></span>
    <span class="quote-line"><span class="quote-line-inner"><em>The trick is making sure it's visible</em></span></span>
    <span class="quote-line"><span class="quote-line-inner"><em>at the right moment.</em></span></span>
  </blockquote>
  <p class="quote-source">Vishnu Sudhan · 2026</p>
</section>

<style>
  .quote-section {
    padding: 96px var(--gutter) 96px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .quote-marks {
    position: absolute;
    top: 24px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(72px, 12vw, 130px);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--accent-faint);
    font-style: italic;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .quote-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    max-width: max-content;
  }
  .quote-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 16px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .quote-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3.4vw, 36px);
    line-height: 1.32;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    max-width: 880px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .quote-text em { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }
  .quote-line { display: block; overflow: hidden; }
  .quote-line-inner {
    display: inline-block;
    transform: translateY(110%);
    transition: transform 0.95s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .quote-line:nth-child(1) .quote-line-inner { transition-delay: 0.05s; }
  .quote-line:nth-child(2) .quote-line-inner { transition-delay: 0.15s; }
  .quote-line:nth-child(3) .quote-line-inner { transition-delay: 0.25s; }
  .quote-line:nth-child(4) .quote-line-inner { transition-delay: 0.35s; }
  .quote-line:nth-child(5) .quote-line-inner { transition-delay: 0.45s; }
  .quote-text.is-revealed .quote-line-inner { transform: translateY(0); }

  .quote-source {
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .quote-section { padding: 64px var(--gutter); }
    .quote-marks { font-size: 80px; top: 18px; }
    .quote-text { font-size: clamp(20px, 5.4vw, 26px); }
  }
</style>
